            <li>Reverse engineer or attempt to extract the source code</li>
            <li>Use the app for any unlawful purpose</li>
            <li>Remove any copyright or proprietary notices</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Subscriptions -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Subscriptions & Payments</h2>

          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-2">Billing</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 space-y-1 mb-4">
            <li>Subscriptions are billed through Apple App Store or Google Play Store</li>
            <li>Payment is charged to your App Store or Play Store account</li>
            <li>Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-2">Free Trials</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            If offered, free trials automatically convert to paid subscriptions unless cancelled before the trial ends. Unused portions of free trials are forfeited upon subscription purchase.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300 mb-2">Cancellation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            You may cancel your subscription at any time through your App Store or Play Store account settings. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. No refunds are provided for partial periods.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- User Content -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Your Content</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            You retain ownership of all content you create or scan using our apps. We do not claim any rights to your scans, text, or other content.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            You are responsible for ensuring you have the right to scan and process any documents or images you use with our apps.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Third-Party Services -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            Our apps may use third-party services for functionality:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Google Gemini API:</strong> For text extraction (OCR). Subject to <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white hover:underline">Google's Terms of Service</a>.</li>
            <li><strong>RevenueCat:</strong> For subscription management. Subject to <a href="https://www.revenuecat.com/terms" class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white hover:underline">RevenueCat's Terms</a>.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Disclaimers -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Disclaimers</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-4">
            Our apps are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied, including but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 space-y-1">
            <li>Accuracy of text extraction results</li>
            <li>Uninterrupted or error-free operation</li>
            <li>Fitness for a particular purpose</li>
            <li>Compatibility with all devices</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            To the maximum extent permitted by law, we shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to loss of data, profits, or business opportunities, arising from your use of our apps.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Termination -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your access to our apps at any time, without notice, for conduct that we believe violates these Terms or is harmful to other users, us, or third parties.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Changes -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of our apps after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms. We encourage you to review this page periodically.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Governing Law -->
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of England and Wales, without regard to conflict of law principles.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
            For questions about these Terms: <a href="mailto:sambulosenda@gmail.com" class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white hover:underline">sambulosenda@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
